Installation instructions for Samba-VirusFilter VFS modules
======================================================================

Basic install procedure
======================================================================

  $ ./configure --with-samba-source=/path/to/samba-3.2.x/source
  ...
  $ make
  ...
  # su -
  Password: xxxxxxxx
  # make install
  ...

Requirements
======================================================================

  * Samba 3.2 source tree
  * Samba build environment

